{"tid":406030,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「末代港獨」彭定康：港獨不可行但不應禁止討論","createTime":"2017-09-19T10:16:07.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-19T13:36:45.000Z","uid":41351,"like":12,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"81b4db65fe2b8730ae3d928c746f7ba26693311c","tid":406030,"uid":41351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T10:16:07.000Z","msg":"前港督彭定康今午出席外國記者協會午餐會時發表演說，指自己三周前曾去信行政長官林鄭月娥，希望她能做更多事情團結香港。他又表示，希望香港不同意見人士能作出對話，但不應作出殺害他人等仇恨言論。<br />\n<br />\n對於近日大學校園的港獨討論及早前出現恭喜官員喪子的標語，他指任何一種自由都並非完全自由，奚落死者家人或揚言殺害他人是不正確的事，希望各方討論時應予以克制。他又認為港獨標語事件屬大學管理範圍，應由校方處理，希望社會各界尊重院校自主。<br />\n<br />\n他重申港獨並不可行，但以《基本法》禁止安樂死及同性婚姻為例，指事件違法，但不等於要禁止討論。<br />\n<br />\n至於有意見認為香港進入威權政府時代，他表示不認同，並指香港仍然是亞洲最自由的城市之一，並要看看林鄭月娥能做到甚麼。<br />\n<a href=\"http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1016954/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1016954%2F&d=uCQ6Vet1%2F7TJztx0FKYDatU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=0a35d2e0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1016954%2F&h=d506c88e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1016954/</a>"},{"pid":"58f04f3837a3fa9c5754f40b988264bdb280cd71","tid":406030,"uid":22858,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T10:17:50.000Z","msg":"咁維持現狀就可行 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22c31a576cd1e54b8f1c018a215d4ccb312c8788","tid":406030,"uid":73092,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T10:20:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁維持現狀就可行 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n英國奶共好耐喇現象先知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"869f9ec918b5c347fbea3114b94f218cd41a46c4","tid":406030,"uid":73092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T10:22:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>咁維持現狀就可行 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n英國奶共好耐喇現<del>象</del>在先知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"58356672c95aaffd14f73d0503597bc91bfd6a12","tid":406030,"uid":79563,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T10:34:36.000Z","msg":"彭定康都ON<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n就係因為港獨係可行, 支那國先咁撚驚呀"},{"pid":"a47ede0e589bbe83892c97ed4e79ce97b18af192","tid":406030,"uid":41351,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T11:09:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>彭定康都ON<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n就係因為港獨係可行, 支那國先咁撚驚呀</blockquote><br />\n點樣可行、連英國佬都唔幫港獨"},{"pid":"72b84e26610d76d99392a07fe6abdd294eb3aec2","tid":406030,"uid":17682,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T11:11:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 彭定康approve講港獨"},{"pid":"b633d8b241cf8bed9f1c76eb9b65c8e313a553e3","tid":406030,"uid":54876,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T11:13:38.000Z","msg":"英國佬，9up當秘笈，講句野都懶係轉番兩三個圈，所以咪衰落囉"},{"pid":"110dd9503eafe48146832146593840701bab09fa","tid":406030,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T11:19:18.000Z","msg":"以佢身份<br />\n<br />\n講到咁算係咁"},{"pid":"84f932ac0a2420b573c2a0008130ab2184b5dd98","tid":406030,"uid":43189,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T11:21:19.000Z","msg":"你咁問佢緊係話唔支持啦，正如你問美國佢都唔會話支持架啦"},{"pid":"8e1b26be218e65244ac20abcadd02fddb376afcf","tid":406030,"uid":41351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T11:25:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你咁問佢緊係話唔支持啦，正如你問美國佢都唔會話支持架啦</blockquote><br />\n中國，英國每年千億貿易，英國政府最現實<br />\n所以肥彭成日鬧政府奶共"},{"pid":"476dbc0b90623bbf5662d3a954cb16e2bc538c5b","tid":406030,"uid":13724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T11:34:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你咁問佢緊係話唔支持啦，正如你問美國佢都唔會話支持架啦</blockquote><br />\n根本問全世界政府都唔會話支持，但你唔指名道姓問佢哋就會話人民應該有選擇權"},{"pid":"303d7ea15ec1c1ba8b3a7bcb3a2340dfda05fdfd","tid":406030,"uid":18818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T11:39:30.000Z","msg":"今次老彭錯喇<br />\n<br />\n就係因為港獨可行<br />\n所以大陸先至禁止討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d529cb667d3122ba7bfcb1f6bdcedafd27ff336d","tid":406030,"uid":5303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T12:56:39.000Z","msg":"彭定康幾時會變過街老鼠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成日出黎話港獨唔可行"},{"pid":"7216d795b459a3dbf5fc63e6959c7b190787fd51","tid":406030,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T12:58:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49360d8cf181129e38ba0824520b667df6fa92ee","tid":406030,"uid":56878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T13:05:55.000Z","msg":"tvb: 他指任何一種自由都並非完全自由，奚落死者家人，希望各方討論時應予以克制。"},{"pid":"037cd663d92cfb636840b6ff93a0a7d3e21bf82b","tid":406030,"uid":73092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T13:26:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>彭定康幾時會變過街老鼠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成日出黎話港獨唔可行</blockquote><br />\n點會變，一日有班人奶英一日都唔會變<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2e148d2993efe04a2e61b8936ac04e8fca1ade6","tid":406030,"uid":132038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T13:35:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b7cc38fb0baf5acfc60b6bcf6a4b7af08b5e7783","tid":406030,"uid":132038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T13:36:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}